{"tid":1162582,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓失聲","createTime":"2019-05-20T03:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T17:43:56.000Z","uid":22701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7387464a2d00d968dc468496ec830d7d139967","tid":1162582,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"上星期隻貓把聲已經有的沙啞, 已經帶佢睇左醫生, 驗埋血所有指數都正常, 無其他病徵,醫生開左的消炎藥俾佢話可能喉嚨發炎, 食晒的藥都唔見好轉, 今朝直頭有的失聲, 有幾下叫唔出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其間食(食罐頭)同痾都正常, 係完全唔飲水要逼佢飲, 呢兩日成日匿係角落頭唔出來, 究竟佢咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca2980803e7094b986e5f7727ebca943d164716","tid":1162582,"uid":195920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"想呃多啲罐頭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09c746a734ade20a4d26cde2680822490e723a5","tid":1162582,"uid":243635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"有D貓感冒後會永久失聲"},{"pid":"ec3c40247a13fcd59c4544d3ee874bb559b3e80e","tid":1162582,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a09c746a734ade20a4d26cde2680822490e723a5","tid":1162582,"uid":243635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"有D貓感冒後會永久失聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"唔係掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過今日又好似好返的，叫得出聲不過變左老牛聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a488fded5def8fad5326b0b7b54867393b91923f","tid":1162582,"uid":103794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"睇過另一個獸醫啦仲等!"},{"pid":"9bf14c367789b42a8f2329ef61f3b44504700008","tid":1162582,"uid":103794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"貓貓有唔妥先至會匿埋<br />\n 連登冇獸醫 直接帶去睇獸醫啦"}]}